5-20210311.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1580095-20210311.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=XsjoyflP4JPXBkuZaWCkHbXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=af8e03e9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1580095-20210311.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=354f2d11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1580095-20210311.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T16:10:32.000Z","msg":"幾多頭家散咗，幾多人要傷心地離開呢個家園，捨小家為大家？切腹都唔夠啦！"},{"pid":"a6252f20f8cf8d552dd1ac3101a64713653d634d","tid":2442531,"uid":61604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T16:12:36.000Z","msg":"又說，去年美國將她和12名特區官員，以及中央官員列入制裁名單，令家人受影響<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n開頭又話冇影響？"},{"pid":"7f03f17001b012831e10129416fca9f4c06da724","tid":2442531,"uid":80724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae1d37a7265b3bc058fec730453f24e61a49a147","tid":2442531,"uid":8171,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T12:03:35.000Z","msg":"英國褫奪淋病一家英國籍就好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T16:14:26.000Z","msg":"有無都無分別，根本出唔到國<br />\n最後返去英國住嘅機會佢幾年前已經放棄咗"},{"pid":"ecf73a0bfa85c4b0c38b0a1ddbf8e904a48c955f","tid":2442531,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T16:15:11.000Z","msg":"香港特首以一副收害者姿態挑釁外國政客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3238bbc7f381ad57f52676cbc0e62b54e569f04a","tid":2442531,"uid":141268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T16:16:35.000Z","msg":"美元結算...."},{"pid":"ce491743e510217b9197bef1f9323033132b94fb","tid":2442531,"uid":107681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T16:17:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LRt